name: RUA
description:
[PHYSICAL AVAILABLE TO FIRST COLLECTOR]

RUA is Te Reo for 'Two' - this is the second in a collection of framed mountainscapes, crafted by Hailtree in Aotearoa.

RUA is approx 8x10" and framed in a black metal frame.

Have you ever sat with a cup of tea, watching the storms roll through the mountains surrounding your home? There's nothing quite like it. So present. The air is so cold and crisp.

[Please contact me after purchase to arrange shipping this to you, shipping available worldwide]
